release.body:
<!-- Release notes generated using configuration in .github/release.yml at 3.9.x -->

## What's Changed

### Modules Upgrades

- Bump micronaut-azure to 4.1.1 (#9265)
- Bump micronaut-gcp to 4.10.2 (#9266)
- Bump micronaut-sql to 4.8.1 (#9262)
- Bump micronaut-kubernetes to 4.0.1 (#9261)
- Bump micronaut-aws to 3.17.2 (#9254)

### Bug Fixes 🐞
* Use the bean definition type as the bean type for custom scopes. by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9233

### GraalVM 🏆
* Fix GraalVM error on JDK 21 by @graemerocher in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9213

### Other Changes 💡
* Fixed the startup url print by @filip-filipovic in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9177
* Reworked ability to disable initializing Slf4J by @altro3 in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9185

### ✅ Tests
* adds Controller Constraint Handler test by @sdelamo in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9245

## New Contributors
* @filip-filipovic made their first contribution in https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/pull/9177

**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/compare/v3.9.1...v3.9.2
